      "side": 1,
      "message": "[error] Line 109: The macOS-specific assignment replaces LOCAL_HOSTVARS with only MACOSX_DEPLOYMENT_TARGET, so the libvpx configure invocation no longer receives the standard HOSTVARS toolchain environment on macOS. That can select host tools/compilers instead of the intended contrib toolchain and matches the current macOS build failure risk. Preserve HOSTVARS when adding the deployment target.\n\n```suggestion\nLOCAL_HOSTVARS\u003d$(HOSTVARS) MACOSX_DEPLOYMENT_TARGET\u003d$(MIN_OSX_VERSION)\n```",
